{"tid":623191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普：將向美國農民提供補償","createTime":"2018-04-09T18:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T12:25:31.000Z","uid":147314,"like":118,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"162338a8f05d2b3daead225e6b823a403c162abf","tid":623191,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T18:59:39.000Z","msg":"川普：將向美國農民提供補償<br />\n<br />\n農民會比以往過得更好<br />\n<br />\nTrump to farmers amid trade war: 'We'll make it up' to you<br />\n<br />\n'The farmers will be better off than they ever were,' the president said.<br />\n<br />\nBy QUINT FORGEY 04/09/2018 12:40 PM EDT<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/story/2018/04/09/trump-trade-war-farmers-509928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fstory%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2Ftrump-trade-war-farmers-509928&d=rt6lTYIo5Ld7Bxv0KkJlZIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=90a7c392\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/story/2018/04/09/trump-trade-war-farmers-509928</a><br />\n<br />\n川普：不要試圖攻擊農民來攻擊我<br />\n<br />\nTrump to China : don't try to attack farmers to attack me<br />\n<br />\nPresident Donald Trump on Monday attempted to reassure American farmers staring down market uncertainty amid an escalating trade dispute with China, which has threatened to level hefty tariffs on soybeans and other agricultural goods.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We&rsquo;ll make it up to them,&rdquo; Trump told reporters ahead of a meeting with his Cabinet. &ldquo;The farmers will be better off than they ever were. It will take a little while to get there, but it could be very quick, actually.<br />\n<br />\n中西部農民是偉大的愛國者<br />\n<br />\nTrump said the midwestern growers are &ldquo;great patriots&rdquo; who &quot;understand that they're doing this for the country.&rdquo; The president also reminded members of the media that he has instructed Agriculture Secretary Sonny Perdue to work with Cabinet officials to shield farmers from China&rsquo;s trade actions.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/story/2018/04/09/trump-trade-war-farmers-509928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fstory%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2Ftrump-trade-war-farmers-509928&d=rt6lTYIo5Ld7Bxv0KkJlZIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=90a7c392\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/story/2018/04/09/trump-trade-war-farmers-509928</a>"},{"pid":"a5194e6b41b074068acf863a3a9dc492b716cf75","tid":623191,"uid":147314,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T19:13:29.000Z","msg":"納瓦羅：中國不認錯反攻擊農民 驚醒美國人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/04/GettyImages-632488266-1-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2FGettyImages-632488266-1-600x400.jpg&h=215ca90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(SAUL LOEB/AFP/Getty Images)<br />\n<br />\n白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅週日（4月8日）說，他認為中國對美國進行關稅報復，對於美國人而言是一個當頭棒喝，讓美國人清醒看到中共的蠻橫無理。<br />\n<br />\n「中國沒有（對美國的關稅）做出優雅反應、停止這一切他們正在做的壞事，而是攻擊美國農民，這是多麼諷刺。我認為這對美國人而言是當頭棒喝。」納瓦羅告訴NBC。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅表示：<span style=\"color: red;\">「我們已經在國家安全策略當中改變對中國的定位，將其定位為戰略競爭者。這是什麼意思？這意味著他們跟我們在經濟繁榮和國家安全方面是競爭者。這是一場總統非常非常嚴肅對待的競爭。」</span><br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅上週在接受國家公共電台採訪的時候說：「我們試圖贏得圍繞未來新興產業的競爭。中共有一個所謂『中國製造2025』的宣言，它闡述了（中共）主導所有新興產業的行動計劃&mdash;&mdash;人工智能、機器人、量子計算等。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果他們通過盜竊我們的東西占領了科技高地，那麼我們作為一個國家，在經濟上、在國家安全上將不會有未來</span>，因為許多這些未來行業有重要的軍事應用。所以川普總統站起來對抗中國是對的。」"},{"pid":"d7427d7d12d3bd43474be36a2bf505abdec2655a","tid":623191,"uid":147314,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T19:20:17.000Z","msg":"納瓦羅在接受國家公共電台採訪的時候，也強烈抨擊中國不承認錯誤的態度。「我認為有意思的是，此刻中共對目前美中關係的反應。<span style=\"color: red;\">它們否認盜竊了我們的知識產權。每個人都知道它們做了。</span>他們否認強迫轉讓我們的技術。」<br />\n<br />\n「中共為了削弱我們的意志和決心，就試圖針對我們的農業領域（徵稅），因為它們認為那樣做可以達到政治目的，（它們認為）川普總統可能不會那麼堅定。」<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅認為，此次跟中國的對壘是川普總統為了美國站起來，反抗中國公然的知識產權盜竊。「中國是一個主權國家，此時此刻有選擇。迄今它選擇否認它所做的事情。全世界都知道它是一個騙子。同時中共也試圖通過瞄準我們經濟當中的某些領域來削弱我們的意志。」<br />\n<br />\n「但是，讓我們記住，我們購買中國的東西比他們購買我們的東西多五倍。如果這件事有任何升級，它們損失的遠遠更多。」"},{"pid":"07a5f1b6d540857775f0d816e4d06250ab483572","tid":623191,"uid":147314,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T19:22:45.000Z","msg":"川普政府和中共最近幾週互相發出關稅威脅。在美國披露對中國500億美元商品徵稅的詳細名單之後，北京宣布對美國500億美元商品徵稅作為報復措施，其中最引人注目的是大豆。<br />\n<br />\n川普然後表示考慮將對華關稅增加兩倍，並強調是美國在懲罰中共。<br />\n<br />\n這些你來我往的關稅威脅引發人們對貿易戰的擔憂。美國中西部議員擔憂關稅將損害種植大豆等莊稼的農民。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅反駁了這些擔憂，指出總統要求農業部部長柏杜（Sonny Perdue）制定計劃，保護美國農民免於關稅帶來的負面影響。"},{"pid":"148139b0e363d062ccb98165d4611e2fc82b6274","tid":623191,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T19:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44623cd738a933cbdad09bde81a225af2c194004","tid":623191,"uid":4783,"like":117,"dislike":3,"score":114,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T19:59:01.000Z","msg":"侵侵真係好鬼叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔可以否認佢呢種性格係政治路上幫佢好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c1aed5699fac5b6f6b9dfd39fa2ecca3cefa69","tid":623191,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T21:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc87d21da553faebfc3ab7ca6ed6a065bdbb5ce","tid":623191,"uid":147314,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T21:36:16.000Z","msg":"侵侵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9c4c7f1ffb0c3dee5e0b9f6d4107ea3ba58a5d","tid":623191,"uid":99205,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T21:42:13.000Z","msg":"養蜂人最慘，俾支那做假搞到收左皮"},{"pid":"4fb669e71f1716fd74c4ec6e5f803b1783e1d7c2","tid":623191,"uid":116054,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T21:57:32.000Z","msg":"早排啲五毛衝出嚟話人炒車， 成日想用炒車呢招 stop 人topic 真係好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061d166be